Introduction

Kim Woojin is a South Korean singer-songwriter under Kustomade. He is a former member of the boy group Stray Kids.

On October 27, 2019, JYP Entertainment announced Woojin's departure from Stray Kids and the agency due to personal circumstances.

Following his departure from Stray Kids, on August 5th, 2021, Kim Woojin made his official debut with the release of his debut album "The moment: 未成年, a minor".

The name of Kim Woojin's fandom is "CUBS" meaning Baby Bear.

Woojin enlisted in the miltary January 20, 2025 and will be discharged July 19,2025.
